leagueMatchEvent.name: Dualies at Ten Paces
leagueMatchEvent.desc:
Enter a battlefield filled with slippery
customers in this all-dualies war!
leagueMatchEvent.regulation:
Stick and move with the best of 'em in this dualies dustup!

・ Players can only choose different varieties of dualies.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

leagueMatchEvent.name: Full Stream Ahead
leagueMatchEvent.desc:
Stampede over your opponents with even
faster rollers and brushes!
leagueMatchEvent.regulation:
Rollers and brushes move faster than ever. The ink race is on!

・ Players can only choose different varieties of rollers or brushes.
・ All players have greatly increased ink speed.
・ Ink consumption while inking will also be greatly increased for all players.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.
